Package com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.gui.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Task
    A functional interface used to allow EventListeners to run pieces of code when they are triggered.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlinkEvent
    An event that is injected whenever the menu cursor blinks.
    ClickEvent<T extends Button<?>>
    The base class for all ClickEvents.
    DataPacket
    A packet of data provided to EventListeners when they are triggered.
    Event
    The base class for all Events.
    GamepadEventGenerator
    A singleton class that generates all gamepad events.
    LoopEvent
    An event that is thrown once at the beginning of each event loop.
    OnClickEvent
    An event that is injected whenever a boolean button is clicked.
    OnClickReleaseEvent
    An event that is injected whenever a boolean button is released.
    TaskPacket<T>
    A packet of tasks.
    WhileClickEvent
    An event that is injected while a boolean button is pressed.
